<h2>You have a friend invitation!</h2>

<p>Hi there,</p>

<p><strong><%= @inviter.name %></strong> wants to be your friend on Joffre!</p>

<p style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
  <a href="<%= accept_invitation_via_email_url(token: @invitation.token) %>" 
     style="background-color: #007bff; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block; margin: 0 10px;">
    Accept Invitation
  </a>
  
  <a href="<%= decline_invitation_via_email_url(token: @invitation.token) %>" 
     style="background-color: #6c757d; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block; margin: 0 10px;">
    Decline
  </a>
</p>

<p>Or visit Joffre directly and use their friend code: <strong><%= @inviter.user_code %></strong></p>

<p>Happy gaming!</p>
<p>The Joffre Team</p>
